summary: A medical professional with 8+ years of clinical experience with a focus on cardiology, general medicine, and telehealth. In the Netherlands, she is currently working as a case manager at HelloDoc responsible for triaging patients in their care pathways and case documentation. In addition, she is providing clinical consultancy services to healthcare companies. She is fully proficient in multiple languages, including Dutch, Russian, English, Pashto, Urdu, and Punjabi.
